            <div class="col-md-4">
                <h3>Travel Insurance</h3>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <div class="page-wrapper">
                <div class="white-bg">
                 
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="">
                            <div class="form-group custom-form-group">

                                <table border=0 style="font-size:large;">
                                    <tr>
                                        <td align="justify">
                                            The new Group Travel Insurance policy has been initiated with M/s. Thomas Cook and the policy is active from 06th March 2018. The policy provider is M/s. Bajaj Allianz General Insurance Company Pvt., Ltd.,
